{"tid":1872991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉湖銀座有間藥房有貨唔賣 疑似淨係賣比識既人","createTime":"2020-02-10T11:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T00:29:11.000Z","uid":91082,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb788b2531a175542edf665db85bb431b5bf8ea","tid":1872991,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"一粥麵隔離間野 其實都唔知係咪藥房來<br />\n晏就睇到佢入左紙巾貨諗住去買紙巾<br />\n問佢佢話要點貨 六點先賣<br />\n點知六點去到問佢佢又唔出聲 <br />\n再問個女員工話唔賣<br />\n但明明見到有幾個人拎住一條走 <br />\n有一個仲同佢笑笑口講話要柯屎 都唔知係咪識既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲見住個呀叔問佢有無抹手紙 佢話無<br />\n跟住比人發現佢有貨仲要拆左袋 佢都話未點貨唔賣 一卷卷個d紙巾都係咁講 <br />\n個呀叔想拎一條買 個員工叫佢唔好攞未點貨個態度仲好撚差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但明明睇住入邊有幾條友都抽一條行出黎<br />\n員工自留就話姐 擺到明就唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374cdc8a3b2643a55eb6f1b1be6f281520ea6dfb","tid":1872991,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"所以呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebf251e809bb843f3a709551f